<li>I am so sorry for your loss.  Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, I extend my condolences on the passing of your [relationship to deceased].</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you navigate this difficult journey.</li>
<li>Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.  May God give you strength and solace.</li>
<li>May the love and support of those around you help ease your sorrow.</li>
<li>Words cannot express the sadness I feel for your loss.  Please accept my deepest sympathy.</li>
<li>I am so saddened to hear about your loss.  May peace find you soon.</li>
<li>Holding your family in my heart and offering my sincerest condolences.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength to your family during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories of [deceased's name] bring you comfort.</li>
